    {'text': 'That if thou shalt confess with thy mouth the Lord Jesus, and shalt believe in thine heart that God hath raised him from the dead, thou shalt be saved.', 'reference': 'Romans 10:9'},
    {'text': 'As far as the east is from the west, so far hath he removed our transgressions from us.', 'reference': 'Psalm 103:12'},
    {'text': 'And let us consider one another to provoke unto love and to good works.', 'reference': 'Hebrews 10:24'},
    {'text': 'Look at the birds of the air; they do not sow or reap or store away in barns, and yet your heavenly Father feeds them.', 'reference': 'Matthew 6:26'},

    // Day 211-220
