    {'text': 'And the work of righteousness shall be peace; and the effect of righteousness quietness and assurance for ever.', 'reference': 'Isaiah 32:17'},
    {'text': 'Blessed is he whose transgression is forgiven, whose sin is covered.', 'reference': 'Psalm 32:1'},
    {'text': 'Do not be anxious about anything, but in every situation, by prayer and petition, with thanksgiving, present your requests to God.', 'reference': 'Philippians 4:6'},
    {'text': 'And thou shalt love the Lord thy God with all thine heart, and with all thy soul, and with all thy might.', 'reference': 'Deuteronomy 6:5'},
    {'text': 'My soul, wait thou only upon God; for my expectation is from him.', 'reference': 'Psalm 62:5'},
    {'text': 'For the Spirit God gave us does not make us timid, but gives us power, love and self-discipline.', 'reference': '2 Timothy 1:7'},
    {'text': 'Blessed are the merciful: for they shall obtain mercy.', 'reference': 'Matthew 5:7'},
