    {'text': 'Brethren, I count not myself to have apprehended: but this one thing I do, forgetting those things which are behind, and reaching forth unto those things which are before.', 'reference': 'Philippians 3:13'},
    {'text': 'Trust in him at all times; ye people, pour out your heart before him: God is a refuge for us.', 'reference': 'Psalm 62:8'},
    {'text': 'Remember ye not the former things, neither consider the things of old. Behold, I will do a new thing.', 'reference': 'Isaiah 43:18-19'},
