    {'text': 'If we live in the Spirit, let us also walk in the Spirit.', 'reference': 'Galatians 5:25'},
    {'text': 'Then they cried unto the Lord in their trouble, and he delivered them out of their distresses.', 'reference': 'Psalm 107:6'},

